Class BaseDrive

  • java.lang.Object
    • frc.robot.SuperClasses.BaseDrive
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BaseDriveHDrive

    public abstract class BaseDrive
extends java.lang.Object
    The base class for any 2 or 3 motor sided drive train that has multiple subclasses.
